OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start this morning but
OL,6,Fcoastal showers will spread inland.
OL,7,FSkies then turning increasingly cloudy
OL,8,Fthroughout the afternoon with some
OL,9,Ffurther rain at times, especially
OL,10,Ftowards the west. Lighter winds
OL,11,Finitially but strengthening again
OL,12,Flater.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FOften cloudy this evening and
OL,15,Fovernight with further patchy rain and
OL,16,Fdrizzle, especially over the hills. A
OL,17,Fband of heavier rain then arriving
OL,18,Finto Cornwall later. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
