OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSome early brightness possible
OL,6,Fin the east, but rain in the west will
OL,7,Fspread across the region. Turning
OL,8,Fdrier and brighter later in the day
OL,9,Fwith winds also gradually easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,12,Flargely fine and dry weekend as high
OL,13,Fpressure builds in. Feeling pleasant
OL,14,Fin any sunshine and lighter winds.
OL,15,FLikely to remain similar early next
OL,16,Fweek as high pressure dominates.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
